.Dd $Mdocdate: August 6 2022 $
.Dt APLDMA 4 arm64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm apldma
.Nd Apple DMA controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "apldma* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the DMA controller integrated on various
Apple SoCs.
.Pp
The controller is used to support DMA for the audio interfaces
integrated on the SoC.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr aplmca 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
.Ox
support for
.Nm
first appeared in
.Ox 7.1 .
